</head>

<body>
    <div class="sficon">
        <img src="../static/icon.jpg" alt="">
        <p>StrangeFlix</p>
        <form action="/home/search" method="post" class="form-search">
            <i class="fa fa-search" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <input class="search" type="text" placeholder="Search" aria-label="Search">
        </form>
        <div class="dropdown">
            <button class="btn  dropdown-toggle" type="button" id="dropdownMenuButton" data-toggle="dropdown"
                aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false"><i class="fa fa-user-secret"></i>
            </button>
            <div class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="dropdownMenuButton">
                <a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Profile</a>
                <a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Settings</a>
                <hr>
                <a class="dropdown-item" href="#"><i class="fa fa-sign-out"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mid">
        <div class="player">
            <video class="player__video viewer" src="../static/videos/b.mp4"
                poster="../static/img/3515433-endgamedek.jpg"></video>

            <div class="player__controls">
                <div class="progress">
                    <div class="progress__filled"></div>
                </div>
                <button class="player__button">
                    <p class="fa fa-step-backward">
                </button>
                <button class="player__button toggle" id="play-btn" title="Toggle Play">â–º</button>
                <button class="player__button">
                    <p class="fa fa-step-forward">
                </button>
                <span class="vol">vol</span>
                <input type="range" name="volume" class="player__slider" min="0" max="1" step="0.05" value="1">
                <span class="speed">speed</span>
                <input type="range" name="playbackRate" class="player__slider" min="0.5" max="2" step="0.1" value="1">
                <span class="current">00:00</span> / <span class="duration">00:00</span>
                <button data-skip="-10" class="player__button">
                    <p class="fa fa-fast-backward">
                </button>
                <button data-skip="10" class="player__button">
                    <p class="fa fa-fast-forward"></p>
                </button>
                <button class="fullscreen-btn">
                    <p class="fa fa-expand"></p>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="like">
            <p>Avengers:End Game</p>
            <div class="likebar">

                <div class="dropdown" id="description">
                    <button class="btn btn-white dropdown-toggle" type="button" id="dropdownMenuButton"
                        data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">Description
                    </button>
                    <div class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="dropdownMenuButton">
                        <p>Thiller</p>
                        <p>Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Tempore, mollitia, beatae, fugiat distinctio quos tenetur nam ab temporibus sequi sed tempora dicta! Facere nihil eaque et nam obcaecati. Unde, impedit.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="cat">
                    <form action="home/video/like" method="post" class="like-btn">
                        <button type="submit"><i class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up">100</i></button>
                    </form>
    
                    <form action="home/video/dislike" method="post" class="like-btn">
                        <button type="submit"><i class="fa fa-thumbs-o-down">12</i></button>
                    </form>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>


    <script src="../static/fe_js/vid-player.js"></script>

    <script src="../static/fe_js/streaming.js"></script>
